<td width="100%"><font size="2">Test Server, April 26th, 2004<br><br>Hot Spots&#33;<br><br>Try out the new Hot Spot zones which give a boost to Experience while adventuring in them. The current Hot Spots are:<br><br>The Castle of Mistmoore<br>The Lair of the Splitpaw<br>Dulak&#39;s Harbor<br>The Tower of Frozen Shadow<br>The Gulf of Gunthak<br>Hate&#39;s Fury<br>The Crypt of Nadox<br>The Torgiran Mines<br><br>The Hot Spot zones will shift from time to time, so watch for messages giving clues as to where the new ones may be.<br><br>Good luck&#33;</font><br><br></td>
